WEBVTT

1
00:59:57.140 --> 00:59:59.540 
1918年出生
Born 1918.

2
00:59:59.700 --> 01:00:01.730 
在雨中被埋葬
Buried in the rain.

3
01:00:01.910 --> 01:00:03.770 
被谋杀
Murdered.

4
01:00:03.940 --> 01:00:07.970 
这就是我们的报应吗？连朋友都没有？
Is that what happens to us? No time for friends?

5
01:00:08.910 --> 01:00:12.080 
只有我们的敌人前来献花
Only our enemies leave roses.

6
01:00:12.380 --> 01:00:15.290 
充满暴力的人生为暴力终结
Violent lives ending violently.

7
01:00:17.260 --> 01:00:22.320 
布莱克早就明白，野蛮是人类的天性
Blake understood. Humans are savage in nature.

8
01:00:22.490 --> 01:00:25.190 
不管你怎样的掩饰…
No matter how much you try to dress it up...

9
01:00:25.360 --> 01:00:27.490 
伪装…
... to disguise it...

10
01:00:27.670 --> 01:00:30.790 
布莱克早已看过了社会的真实面貌
... Blake saw society's true face.

